 &UR; BUSINESS: &LR;  SAN FRANCISCO _ The Bay Area is more than a leader in
computer chips, the Internet and multimedia. It's also a major
center for mural artists. From San Jose to Sebastopol, San
Francisco to Pleasanton, 47 mural businesses are listed in local
phone books compared with 43 around New York City and 37 each in
the Los Angeles and Chicago metropolitan areas. &UR; BY PETER SINTON &LR;
