<DOCNO> NYT20000906.0033 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-06 02:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2765 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-BBA-REDSOX-A'S-BOS &LR;      09-06 0892
