<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-06 10:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3631 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i BC-PIRACY-ASIA-ART-2TAKE     09-06 1219
