   FOOD-CUPCAKES _ A cupcake for every occasion: There's no more
complete, petite package of pleasure than cupcakes. This time of
year, there'll be plenty of occasions, from class celebrations to
birthday parties, for these neat, no-fuss treats. And they aren't
just for kids -- we offer some cupcakes for coffee breaks and
after-dinner moments as well. Plus baking and decorating
