<P>
   The New York Times is planning a package of articles on events
connected with the Millennium Summit meeting at the United Nations.
Articles will include:
</P>
<P>
   U.N.-CLINTON (United Nations) - The ledeall on the Millennium
Summit meeting and President Clinton's address. By David E. Sanger.
</P>
<P>
