<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-06 14:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4030 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r f BC-AUTO-GM-SUVS-HNS &LR;      09-06 1198
