There is so much talking and hooting, so much popcorn flying, so
much soda spilling down the aisles, you wonder why you bothered.
Tempting as it may be, don't talk to the person you're with. Clean
up your refuse at the end.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Amy Vanderbilt Complete Book of Etiquette by Nancy Tuckerman
and Nancy Dunnan
</P>
