<P>
   HISPANICS-BUYINGPOWER _ The University of Georgia releases a
national study that shows rapid increases in the buying power of
Hispanics and Asians in Georgia and other states in the Southeast.
Only 2-3 states had more rapid increases in buying power than
Georgia. Why? An ever-hungry economy that absorbs workers as soon
as they arrive and has propelled many immigrants into the middle
class. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 17.
