<TEXT>
<P>
   The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following business
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Thursday, Sept. 7, and thereafter. For more information, contact
Carol Bidwell at the Daily News, (818) 713-3702.
</P>
<P>
   LITTON-EARNINGS (Los Angeles) _ Litton announces strong
fourth-quarter earnings Wednesday, beating estimates, but its
forecast of pared-down earnings in the next quarter drives down its
stock price 23 percent in early trading. (By Robert Monroe) Will
also move on ``a'' national news wire.
</P>
