love its efficient, boxy ice-resurfacing machines, which has a top
speed of nine miles an hour. Zamboni's Website is chuck full of
information and is one of the most enjoyable to view. A Zamboni in
action during a hockey game between the New Jersey Devils and the
Philadelphia Flyers in 1998. (G. Paul Burnett/The New York Times)
</P>
